    <main>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>FAQs</h1>
        <ul>
            <li class="faq">
                <div class="question">
                    What is NoteEase?
                    <span class="icon-main">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="answer non-active">
                    NoteEase is a user-friendly note creating website that allows you to effortlessly capture, organize, and manage your thoughts, ideas, and information. It's a versatile platform designed for students, professionals, creatives, and anyone who values efficient note-taking.
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="faq">
                <div class="question">
                    Is NoteEase free to use?
                    <span class="icon-main">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p class="answer non-active">
                    Yes, NoteEase offers a free plan that provides access to basic note-taking features. However, for users seeking advanced functionalities and additional storage capacity, we also offer premium subscription plans at affordable prices.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="faq">
        <div class="question">
            Can I access my notes from different devices?
            <span class="icon-main">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
            </span>
        </div>
        <p class="answer non-active">
            Absolutely! NoteEase is designed for seamless synchronization across all your devices. Whether you're using a computer, tablet, or smartphone, your notes will be accessible whenever and wherever you need them.
        </p>
    </li>
    <li class="faq">
        <div class="question">
            How secure are my notes on NoteEase?
            <span class="icon-main">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
            </span>
        </div>
        <p class="answer non-active">
            We take your data security seriously. NoteEase employs robust encryption and follows industry best practices to ensure your notes and personal information are kept secure and private. Rest assured that your data is in safe hands
        </p>
    </li>
</ul>
</div>
    </main>
<script>
    const faqs = document.querySelectorAll(".faq");
    for (const item of faqs) {
        const curr_faq = item.childNodes;
        console.log(curr_faq);
        const question = curr_faq[1];
        const answer = curr_faq[3];
        const icon = question.querySelector(".icon-main");
        icon.addEventListener("click", function () {
            answer.classList.toggle("non-active");
            const i = icon.querySelector("i");
            i.classList.toggle("fa-xmark");
            i.classList.toggle("fa-plus");
        });
    }
</script>
